# Environment Variables for BizCore360

# OpenAI API Key - Get this from https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# For local development:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Replace sk-your-openai-api-key-here with your actual OpenAI API key
# 3. Run: npm run dev
# 4. Open http://localhost:3000/polls-setup.html

# For Vercel deployment:
# 1. Go to Vercel Dashboard > Your Project > Settings > Environment Variables
# 2. Add OPENAI_API_KEY with your actual API key
# 3. Set Environment to "Production" (and "Preview" if needed)
# 4. Redeploy your project